title: Will the Rams Go Undefeated?
itunes:title: Will the Rams Go Undefeated?
description:
The Good Morning Football Crew decides whether or not the Rams will go undefeated (00:38). The gang also discusses what their Dream Trades would be (22:55). Lastly, Kay Adams, Nate Burleson, Peter Schrager, and Kyle Brandt give you a new segment called Bard Knocks (27:01). Be sure to check in every Wednesday to the GMFB podcast! Like, share, subscribe!
